WEBVTT

00:01:02.160 --> 00:01:06.056
The Central African Republic
is a country of about five million people

00:01:06.080 --> 00:01:07.576
the size of Texas

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:08.880
in the center of Africa.

00:01:10.240 --> 00:01:14.560
The country has known chronic violence
since French colonial rule ended in 1960.

00:01:16.440 --> 00:01:18.376
The war I reported on

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.520
was between the minority
Muslim government,

00:01:21.520 --> 00:01:22.720
called the Seleka,

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:25.120
and citizen militias,

00:01:26.080 --> 00:01:27.856
mostly Christian,

00:01:27.880 --> 00:01:29.080
called the anti-balaka.